pageProduct.name: Swisse Propolis 2000mg 300 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Ultiboost High Strength Propolis is a premium quality formula containing propolis to support general health and wellbeing.

Replenish The Body: Propolis is used in Traditional Chinese Medicine to replenish the body and support wellbeing. Propolis has been used for centuries in Western and Eastern medicine.

Antioxidant Support: Propolis contains naturally occurring bioflavonoid antioxidants to help protect against free radical damage and support the maintenance of good health.

Swisse Ultiboost High Strength Propolis has been formulated based on scientific and traditional evidence to provide propolis in a high strength, convenient one-a-day dose.

Size: 300 Capsules

Warnings

Propolis may cause allergic reactions. If irritation or swelling of the mouth or throat occurs-discontinue use.

Ingredients

Contains: EACH CAPSULE CONTAINS: PROPOLIS dry extract equiv. to fresh 2g

Allergen Free From: Artificial Flavours| Egg| Gluten| Lactose| Yeast

Directions

One capsule daily or as directed by your healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C. Do not use if cap seal is broken.

Storage Temperature: Store below 25°C.
